How to run scrapy for talking dictionaries:

scrapy crawl alltalkdict -a lang=LANGUAGE 

where LANGUAGE is the name of one of the supported zapotec languages, as it appears in the url

To output to a file, run:

scrapy crawl alltalkdict -a lang=LANGUAGE -o FILENAME.FILEEXTENSION

where FILENAME is the name of the file and FILEEXTENSION is the file extension suffix